{"title":"“新货郎”——给送料员","authors":["易连贵"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":4,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“新货郎”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——给送料员\t鞍山钢铁公司工人　易连贵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车刀、钻头亮光光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"油壶铮亮喷油香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连你那颗滚烫的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐装车上！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你推着货车车间里走呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘿，谁不说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好一个“新货郎”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好一个“新货郎”呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水洒遍机床旁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车间工人几百名，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁需要啥你都记心上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这边机床还没停稳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你把油壶递身旁；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那边卡盘还在飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的车刀又送上。……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好一个“新货郎”呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五金百货车上装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红心牵着货车飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞遍所有机床旁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车间工人几百名，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"齐声来赞扬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千言万语汇一句："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你《为人民服务》学的棒！　〔选自《鞍钢日报》〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}